</caption>
<paragraph id="5E555E77FFDC3345FF52FF6D765FFE92" blockId="4.[166,1225,175,266]" pageId="4" pageNumber="199">
In this paper, I only consider the 
<typeStatus id="8151E0D5FFDC3345FDC3FF6D7048FF52" box="[586,635,175,202]" pageId="4" pageNumber="199">type</typeStatus>
species of the nominal genera, with their synonymy, based on the study of 
